---
layout: full-width.njk
title: Semua Artikel Python - BelajarPython.com
description: Jelajahi koleksi artikel, tips, dan tutorial mendalam tentang Python, Data Science, AI, dan Keamanan Siber.
permalink: /article/
---

<div
    class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero Section Artikel -->
    <section
        class="relative bg-white border-b border-slate-100 overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Decorative background -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none">
            <svg class="w-full h-full" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
                <defs>
                    <pattern id="grid-bg" width="10" height="10" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                        <path d="M 10 0 L 0 0 0 10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"/>
                    </pattern>
                </defs>
                <rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(#grid-bg)"/>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 md:px-10 py-16 md:py-24">
            <div
                class="max-w-3xl">
                <!-- Breadcrumb removed -->
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6">
                    Wawasan &
                    <span class="text-primary-500">Eksplorasi</span>
                    Python
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
                    Kumpulan artikel pilihan mulai dari berita terbaru, tips praktis, hingga pembahasan mendalam seputar teknologi Python
                    dan ekosistemnya.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Article Grid Section -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 md:px-10 py-12 md:py-20">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-10">
            {% for article in collections.articles %}
                <article class="flex">
                    <a
                        href="{{ article.url }}" class="group relative flex flex-col w-full bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] md:rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden border border-slate-200/60 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 ease-out no-underline">
                        <!-- Card Image Wrapper -->
                        <div class="relative aspect-[16/10] overflow-hidden">
                            <img
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700 ease-in-out" src="{{ article.data.image or '/img/logos/logo-belajarpython-square.png' }}" alt="{{ article.data.title }}" loading="lazy"/>
                            <!-- Category Badge -->
                            <div class="absolute top-5 left-5">
                                <span class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest
                                        text-primary-500 shadow-md border border-slate-100/50">
                                    {{ article.data.category or 'ARTIKEL' }}
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <!-- Gradient Overlay -->
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/40 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100
                                transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Card Content -->
                        <div
                            class="p-4 md:p-8 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                            <!-- Title -->
                            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors leading-snug mb-2
                                    md:mb-4 line-clamp-2 group-hover:underline decoration-primary-500 underline-offset-4">
                                {{ article.data.title }}
                            </h3>
                            <!-- Excerpt (optional, if you have one) -->
                            <p class="text-slate-500 line-clamp-2 text-sm md:text-base mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                                {{ article.templateContent | striptags | truncate(120) }}
                            </p>
                            <!-- Card Footer -->
                            <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-slate-50 flex items-center justify-between">
                                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 font-bold text-xs">
                                        BP
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                                        <span class="text-slate-900 font-semibold text-xs">{{ article.url | getMonthYearFromUrl }}</span>
                                        <span class="text-slate-400 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider font-medium">5 Min Read</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary-500
                                        group-hover:border-primary-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
                                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </article>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Newsletter / CTA (Optional but adds premium feel) -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-10 pb-20">
        <div
            class="bg-primary-600 rounded-[2rem] md:rounded-[3rem] p-8 md:p-16 text-center text-white relative overflow-hidden
                shadow-2xl shadow-primary-100">
            <!-- Decorative pattern -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
                <svg class="w-full h-full" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
                    <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="40" fill="currentColor"/>
                    <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="40" fill="currentColor"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 italic">Ingin belajar lebih dalam?</h2>
                <p class="text-primary-100 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    Ikuti seri tutorial langkah-demi-langkah kami yang dirancang khusus untuk pemula hingga profesional.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="/tutorial/apa-itu-python"
                    class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-primary-500 font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-slate-50
                        transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-black/10">
                    Mulai Belajar Sekarang
                    <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>